## DESIGN SYSTEM

### Typography
- Display/headings: "Instrument Serif" or "Playfair Display" (Google Fonts)
- Body: "DM Sans" or "Sora"
- Monospace (for code/skills): "JetBrains Mono"
- NEVER use: Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui

### Color Palette (dark-first)
```css
:root {
  --bg:        #0a0a0a;
  --surface:   #111111;
  --border:    #1f1f1f;
  --text:      #f0ede8;
  --muted:     #6b6b6b;
  --accent:    #e8d5b0;   /* warm gold — change to match your vibe */
  --accent-2:  #4a9eff;   /* electric blue pop */
}
```
→ Override accent colors to match your personality. One dominant, one pop.

### Spacing (8px grid)
- xs: 4px | sm: 8px | md: 16px | lg: 24px | xl: 40px | 2xl: 64px | 3xl: 96px
- Section padding: py-24 to py-32
- Max content width: max-w-5xl (1024px), centered

