## LAYOUT RULES

### Hero Section
- Full viewport height (min-h-screen)
- Name LARGE — clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem)
- Role/tagline below, muted color
- Subtle grid or noise texture background
- Scroll indicator (animated bounce arrow or line)
- NO hero image unless it's a strong portrait — text-first

### Navigation
- Fixed top, backdrop-blur-md, border-b border-border/40
- Logo left (initials or name), links right
- Mobile: hamburger → full-screen overlay menu with stagger animation
- Active link: accent color underline, not bold

### Projects Section
- Grid layout: 2 cols desktop, 1 col mobile
- Each card: dark surface, subtle border, hover lifts + border brightens
- Show: project name, 1-line description, tech stack pills, live/github links
- NO screenshots unless you have good ones — use abstract color blocks instead

### Skills Section
- Horizontal scrolling marquee OR grouped by category
- Use monospace font for skill names
- NO skill bars/percentages — they look amateur

### About Section
- Short paragraph (keep your exact text)
- Maybe a timeline of experience/education
- Minimal — let work speak

### Contact Section
- Simple: email link (large), social icons
- NO contact forms unless you have backend
- Copy email to clipboard on click with toast notification

