## WHAT TO AVOID
- Purple/violet gradients (overused AI aesthetic)
- Glassmorphism everywhere
- Particle.js or canvas particle backgrounds
- Skill percentage bars
- Typewriter text effects
- Centered-everything layouts (use asymmetry)
- Generic stock icons — use Lucide or Phosphor only
- Lazy loading skeleton that flashes too long

